title: For Sale:  Timney... Nuff Said.
location: Northside San Antonio, San Antonio, Texas
postcontent: Letting go of a very lightly used Timney trigger. One of their top models. When you get down to nuts and bolts, Timney really is pretty much the best out there. They’ve been around WAY LONGER than Geiselle, Elftman, or CNC. I’ve had about 30 different aftermarket triggers. I’ve made it my business to try all of the “best” triggers on the market. And this is definitely one of The Best triggers I’ve EVER used. The only reason I’m selling it is because someone bought the rifle it was in and didn’t want to pay for the aftermarket trigger. All of my other rifles have high end triggers installed already so there’s no place for this to go and I don’t need another rifle. The exact model is Timney 661-S (Skeletonized) 3lb Trigger. These go for $242 at their CHEAPEST. The places that offer them for $232 charge $15 for shipping and then tax if they’re in Texas. Trust me i went in and added them to my cart and calculated cheapest shipping method. Or they’re just plain out of stock. Make an offer... but just to set some boundaries, if you offer $150, your shots are hitting below your marl. This isn’t a charity. I’ll get it to you cheaper than anywhere else but I’m not giving you something for nothing. That has become a HUGE problem on this site. People’s god awful lowballing. Your balls don’t hang that low my friend.You want nice things in life? Then sack up and work hard for it and stop asking for handouts. Guess what? You make $25,000 a year, you can’t afford a Ford Raptor. Simple as that. I get it. You want nice things for cheap so you can pretend that you’re a “baller” in front of your friends. Fall in line and work for what you have.Absolutely look for a good deal but there’s a difference between and good dealand getting something for nothing.I don’t expect to get “brand new” price for this but make a reasonable offer.WILL TRADE FOR 1,000 OF BRASS CASED 9mmif you’re Interested in the Trigger and NOT debating semantics, please message me with a MANLY “I work hard for my sh*t and I play hard as well” kind of offer.

title: For Sale:  How To Learn cryptocurrency wallet
postcontent:
A best cryptocurrency wallet is a protected digital wallet utilized to store, send & receive digital currency like Bitcoin. Many coins have an official wallet or a couple of officially advised third-party wallets.
Cryptocurrency itself is not really stored in a wallet. Rather, a private key (safe and secure electronic code recognized just to you & your wallet) is stored that shows ownership of a public key (a public electronic code linked to a particular amount of currency). So your wallet stores your private & public keys, permits you to send and obtain coins, as well as works as a personal ledger of transactions.
There are three type of cryptocurrency wallet for instead, Hardware wallet, Software wallet and Paper wallet.
